dnfs (0.1.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial DKMS package for NFS multipath on Ubuntu 26.04 / Linux 7.0.
  * Bumps NFS_MAX_CONNECTIONS from 16 to 32 for higher per-mount throughput.
  * Includes nfs-stress benchmark tool and ansible deployment playbooks.

